# dist/ is compiled output from src/ (tsc). It must stay committed because the
# plugin is installed straight from this repo with no build step, but it is a
# generated artifact and should never be reviewed or hand-edited.
#
# - linguist-generated: collapses these files in GitHub PR diffs and excludes
#   them from language stats.
# - -diff: suppresses textual diffs so reviewers focus on src/ changes.
#
# CI (.github/workflows/ci.yml) rebuilds dist/ and fails if it differs from the
# committed output, so correctness is guaranteed without manual review.
dist/** linguist-generated=true
dist/** -diff
